import React from 'react'
import Newsapp from './Components/Newsapp/Newsapp'
import Navbar from './Components/Navbar/Navbar'
import { Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <>
  <Navbar />
  <Routes>
    <Route path="/Apple"><Newsapp newsName="iphone" /></Route>
    <Route path="/Tesla"><Newsapp newsName="tesla" /></Route>
    <Route path="/Bitcoin"><Newsapp newsName="bitcoin" /></Route>
    <Route path="/nasa"><Newsapp newsName="nasa" /></Route>
    <Route path="/upsc"><Newsapp newsName="upsc" /></Route>
    </Routes>
  </>


      

  )
}

export default App
